
# 1. 邮件类型

1. 感激
I am writing to express my heartfelt appreciation for the exceptional tour experience I recently had with your company
2. 提诉求 索取sth
I am writing to kindly request an update on the status of my job application and the expected timeline for the decision-making process
3.道歉
I am writing to address the concerns you raised in your recent letter regarding the noise from my residence. Firstly, 
4.汇报
I am writing to inform you about an upcoming event that I am organizing on behalf of our esteemed club
5.求帮助
I'm writing to seek your advice and insights about potential employment opportunities in Singapore, as I am seriously considering the possibility of working there.
6.主动给人家做向导
I am writing to express my thrill beyond words at the prospect of your upcoming visit to our hometown.


7. 提需求 求关注
I am writing to bring to your attention a matter of the utmost importance regarding a certificate that I received upon completing a course at your esteemed institution

8. 投诉
I am writing to bring to your attention an unfortunate incident that has left me quite dissatisfied with your customer service team.

9. 提改善
I am writing to bring to your attention a concern I have regarding the bicycle parking facilities managed by your company at my workplace, which has been impacting my daily commute to work.
10. 申请学校
I am writing to express my keen interest in seeking admission to the xxx course offered by your Institute.
11. 申请工作
I am writing to express my strong interest in the [Job Title] position at [Company Name]
I am writing to express my strong interest in the position advertised by your company for taking care of children
12. 邀请
I am writing to extend an invitation that I hope you will find both exciting and enjoyable



# 2. 重点句
- I hope this letter finds you in good health and high spirits. 
- I would highly value your consideration in addressing this matter at your earliest convenience. 
- I genuinely appreciate your understanding and prompt attention to this matter, and I am confident that your assistance and intervention will greatly help rectify this situation. 
- I want to sincerely apologize for any inconvenience or discomfort this may have caused you and your family. 


# 2. 范文分类

- 2.1 Acknowledgement [done]
I hope this letter finds you in good health and high spirits. 
I am writing to express my heartfelt appreciation for the exceptional tour experience I recently had with your company. The tour, led by one of your guides, was nothing short of outstanding.
I must take a moment to commend this guy. 
Once again, I would like to extend my sincere gratitude to you. The memorable experience provided by you is a testament to your commitment to excellence in the industry.

- 2.2  Enquiry [done]
I am writing to kindly request an update on the status of my job application and the expected timeline for the decision-making process. I fully understand that such processes may take some time to complete, but knowing the outcome is essential for me to make informed decisions regarding my career path.
I would highly value your consideration in addressing this matter at your earliest convenience. 
Please feel free to reach out to me at your convenience via email or by phone for any further information or clarification you may require. 
I look forward to receiving your response and hope for a positive outcome. 
- 2.3 Apology 【done】
I am writing to address the concerns you raised in your recent letter regarding the noise from my residence. Firstly, I want to sincerely apologize for any inconvenience or discomfort this may have caused you and your family. 
Given this situation, I intend to proceed as follows: firstly, a; additionally, b.
Again, your comfort and peace of mind are important to me, and I am dedicated to rectifying this situation promptly. Thank you for your understanding and patience. I look forward to maintaining a harmonious neighborly relationship moving forward.

- 2.4 Report letter [done]
I am writing to inform you about an upcoming event that I am organizing on behalf of our esteemed club
As the organizer of the event, my role encompasses various responsibilities including
I will keep you updated on the progress of the preparations and please feel free to reach out to me at your convenience if you have any questions, suggestions, or if there are any specific areas you would like me to focus on as we approach the event date.
Thank you for your support and I look forward to your valuable insights.

- 2.5 Ask for advice [done]
I'm writing to seek your advice and insights about potential employment opportunities in Singapore, as I am seriously considering the possibility of working there.

I genuinely appreciate your time and assistance with this matter. Your firsthand knowledge and advice are invaluable to me. If there are any particular nuances or cultural insights that you think would be beneficial for me to know, please feel free to share them. 
Please feel free... 
Thank you once again, and I look forward to hearing your thoughts and suggestions. 

- 2.6 介绍信
It brings me immense joy to hear of your interest in visiting my hometown! I assure you, it's a decision you won't regret.
To make the most of your visit, here are a few suggestions:
I'm sure you'll have a fantastic time exploring my hometown. Please feel free to reach out to me for any further information or assistance with your travel plans. I can't wait to catch up, show you around and share the beauty of my hometown with you.
Looking forward to your visit!
- 2.7 Request [done]
I am writing to bring to your attention a matter of utmost importance regarding a certificate that I received upon completing a course at your esteemed institution. Unfortunately, due to unforeseen circumstances, I have misplaced the certificate. 
In light of the above, I kindly request your assistance in reissuing the certificate. I am more than willing to cover any administrative costs associated with this process, and I can provide any necessary information to facilitate its accurate reproduction. I would highly value your consideration in addressing this matter at your earliest convenience. 
I genuinely appreciate your understanding and prompt attention to this matter, and I am confident that your assistance and intervention will greatly help rectify this situation. 
Please feel free to reach out to me at your convenience if there are any specific steps or documentation required from my end to initiate this process. 


- 2.8 Complaint+Request [done]
I am writing to bring to your attention an unfortunate incident that has left me quite dissatisfied with your customer service team.
Yesterday, I was a passenger on one of your buses, traveling from a to b. Unfortunately, during the journey, I realized that I had inadvertently left behind my laptop. This item holds significant personal value to me, and its loss has caused me great distress. Regrettably, my experience with your customer service team when I contacted them about the lost item was far from satisfactory.
In light of this, I kindly request the following actions be taken: ... I would highly value your consideration in addressing this matter at your earliest convenience. 
I would highly appreciate it if you could kindly consider this matter and address it at your earliest convenience.
I genuinely appreciate your understanding and prompt attention to this matter, and I am confident that your assistance and intervention will greatly help rectify this situation. 
Please feel free... Thank you for your time and cooperation. 

- 2.9 Suggestion [done]
I am writing to bring to your attention a concern I have regarding the bicycle parking facilities managed by your company at my workplace, which has been impacting my daily commute to work.
In light of this, I would like to offer the following suggestions to address this issue:
I want to emphasize that my intention is not to criticize, but rather to contribute constructively to the improvement of your operations. I believe that implementing these suggestions will significantly improve the overall experience for cyclists using these facilities. 
I genuinely appreciate your understanding and prompt attention to this matter and am confident that your company's commitment to excellence in parking management will lead to positive changes.
Please feel free... Thank you for your time and consideration. 
I look forward to hearing from you and to witnessing the positive impact of these potential improvements.


- 2.10 Application [done]
I am writing to express my keen interest in seeking admission to the artificial intelligence course offered by your Institute.
I am writing to express my strong interest in the [Job Title] position at [Company Name]
The course is of particular significance to me due to its direct relevance to my professional interests and career goals. Having extensively researched the course content, I am thoroughly impressed by its comprehensive curriculum and the practical skills it aims to impart. This aligns perfectly with my background in computer science. I believe that this course will not only complement my existing knowledge but also equip me with essential tools to excel in my field. 

Please find attached my completed application form and all necessary supporting documents. Thank you for your time and consideration. I am eagerly looking forward to the possibility of being a part of your Institute. 
Please feel free... Thank you for your time and consideration. 

- 2.11 Invitation [done]
I've been thinking about the upcoming holiday season, and the idea of a vacation has been lingering in my mind for quite some time. After some careful consideration, I've come to a decision, and I want to share it with you.

I fully understand that schedules can be hectic, and I completely respect any prior commitments you might have. Nevertheless, if there is any way you can make it, I would be absolutely thrilled to have you accompany me on this vacation.
Please take your time to consider this invitation, and feel free to reach out ... Your presence would truly make this vacation a cherished memory for years to come.
I can't wait to catch up, and I hope that we might even have the opportunity to meet up in person soon. Looking forward to hearing from you, and hopefully, to sharing this adventure together.
